Financial Controller
Offshore Recruitment Services
UAE
Posted on: 29 Apr 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
Responsibilities:
•	Develops financial goals and objectives
•	Manages and oversees general accounting, accounts payable, payroll, property accounting, financial reporting and fixed assets
•	Supervises the areas of accounting/financial reporting, accounts payable, payroll and fixed assets , which includes hiring, training and disciplining employees
•	Ensures that all activities are functioning properly and that appropriate policies and procedures are developed, implemented and maintained to ensure the appropriate accounting and reporting
•	Manages the monthly close process to ensure the timely and accurate accounting and reporting
•	Works with other teams to develop appropriate internal control mechanisms, policies and procedures are in place to ensure that financial activity is accounted-for and reported accurately
•	Maintains and updates Delegation of Authority and ensures all financial transactions are correctly undertaken accordingly
•	Coordinates audit activities
•	Researches new accounting guidelines, undertakes accounting technical interpretations and implements changes to policies and procedures to ensure compliance with appropriate accounting guidelines
•	Maintains active involvement in the Capital Approval Process and allocation and tracking of project funds
•	Provides support for business development initiatives
REQUIREMENTS
To be successful you must be/have:
•	Bachelor Degree as a minimum, MBA/ Professional Qualification will be a huge plus
•	At least 7-10 years of experience with 3-4 years in a similar role in a large reputable organization managing large A/P,
•	Payroll functions
•	Proven Internal Controls experience
•	Experience with accounting systems and developing and implementing accounting policies and procedures
•	Demonstrated managerial skills and ability to provide effective guidance and direction to a management team and staff
•	Strong analytical and interpretative skills
•	Effective communication skills
ABOUT THE COMPANY
Offshore Recruitment Services specialise in the recruitment of in all aspects of offshore vacancies for all levels of permanent, temporary and contract positions.
Whether a client is searching for a highly skilled candidate, looking to head hunt a specific individual, a team of contractors for a project or management of gifted personnel, we are ready and have a proven track record of meeting such requirements.
Offshore Recruitment Services was formed with the specific aim of providing a quality service to link key candidates to our clients. We find the right people for your business.
